show.description: Nadia is the general in the northern border of the empire. With a tough exterior, he is filled with tenderness and deep affection inside. As the empress of the Abyss Kingdom, Aurora's courage, determination, and her fearless attitude towards love inject more vitality into this relationship. After being reborn, as they faced external challenges and misunderstandings together, they always held fast to their love for each other and overcame various difficulties jointly.
